  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >玩法介绍</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款<strong>肉鸽扑克</strong>游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >桌面有3个牌组，你需要每次打3张牌填满这3个牌组。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >牌组会自动根据牌型大小，分成</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >高级牌组</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >中级牌组</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >低级牌组</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >填满后，会自动根据牌型结算积分。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309020/extras/e731d2cf108c58b9f70819582c1379e1.avif?t=1737101367\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309020/extras_big/e731d2cf108c58b9f70819582c1379e1.avif?t=1737101367 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以通过商店购买强力道具，构筑你的道具组。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >道具可以来提升结算的积分，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309020/extras/25370426b2f413fe4049b118b6ff8f71.avif?t=1737101367\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309020/extras_big/25370426b2f413fe4049b118b6ff8f71.avif?t=1737101367 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >另外，还有丰富的任务系统，可以增强你的构筑。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在第4关，第10关，和第16关的时候可以选择一个任务。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成指定任务可以获得特殊奖励，来提升构筑以及容错。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309020/extras/a04b260491f4110c00ffce66f208be27.avif?t=1737101367\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309020/extras_big/a04b260491f4110c00ffce66f208be27.avif?t=1737101367 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >玩法介绍</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款<strong>肉鸽扑克</strong>游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >桌面有3个牌组，你需要每次打3张牌填满这3个牌组。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >牌组会自动根据牌型大小，分成</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >高级牌组</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >中级牌组</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >低级牌组</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >填满后，会自动根据牌型结算积分。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309020/extras/e731d2cf108c58b9f70819582c1379e1.avif?t=1737101367\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309020/extras_big/e731d2cf108c58b9f70819582c1379e1.avif?t=1737101367 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以通过商店购买强力道具，构筑你的道具组。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >道具可以来提升结算的积分，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309020/extras/25370426b2f413fe4049b118b6ff8f71.avif?t=1737101367\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309020/extras_big/25370426b2f413fe4049b118b6ff8f71.avif?t=1737101367 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >另外，还有丰富的任务系统，可以增强你的构筑。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在第4关，第10关，和第16关的时候可以选择一个任务。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成指定任务可以获得特殊奖励，来提升构筑以及容错。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309020/extras/a04b260491f4110c00ffce66f208be27.avif?t=1737101367\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309020/extras_big/a04b260491f4110c00ffce66f208be27.avif?t=1737101367 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
